window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cole is the most powerful witch to ever be born. Except, he’s a man, and there has never been a male witch.</p> <p>Now, Cole is stuck in the Devil’s Academy full of evil women who want to destroy him. To survive, he’ll have to perform a dark ritual that enslaves the beautiful witches to him.</p> <p>They’ll hate serving a man, of course, but that just makes the conquest over their bodies, minds, and souls that much sweeter.</p> <p><b>Disclaimer: </b>This novel contains horrific violence, a harem, and deviant mind control sexual escapades.</p>"; 
